org.chromium.sdk
Interface TabDebugEventListener

public interface TabDebugEventListener

This interface is used by the SDK to report browser-related debug events for a certain tab to the clients.

Method Summary

          Reports a closing event on the target tab.

closed

void closed()
Reports a closing event on the target tab. All following communications with the associated tab are illegal. This call will be followed by call to DebugEventListener.disconnected().
